</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-48_ pf-text-1">The Care Quality Commission (CQC) stipulates that organisations must ensure their staff receive training relevant to their roles and responsibilities, including completing the care certificate where applicable.















































